The iPayX FX Audit MCP server is a toolset for auditing foreign exchange transactions against mid-market rates and generating forensic reports directly within AI assistants [1][2][3]. It acts as a rail-agnostic audit layer for B2B payments, supporting sources like SWIFT, SEPA, and stablecoins [1][2].

To configure the server in your MCP-compatible client, use the following endpoint [1][4]:

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "ipayx-fx": {
      "url": "https://wild-bird-a412.ybolduc.workers.dev/mcp"
    }
  }
}
```

Available tools include audit_fx_fee, compare_providers, score_invoice, and get_mid_market_rate [3]. Use caution with tool outputs; some tools provide qualitative scores while full forensic reports are accessible via the iPayX website [5][6].
